citation: Proclamation under the Fee Units Amendment Act 2023 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Fee Units Amendment Act 2023

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under the Fee Units Amendment Act 2023 fix 1 January 2024 as the day on which that Act commences.

19 December 2023

B.BAKER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

MICHAEL DARREL JOSEPH FERGUSON

Treasurer

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 27 December 2023

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
